@startuml Water Tracking Flow
!theme vibrant
title LilyFit - Water Tracking Flow

actor User
participant "HomeScreen\n(Dashboard)" as Home
participant "WaterTrackerCard" as WaterCard
participant "AppProvider" as Provider
participant "WaterReminderScreen" as ReminderScreen
participant "NotificationService" as Notify
participant "SupabaseService" as Supabase

== View Water Tracker ==

User -> Home: View Dashboard
activate Home

Home -> Provider: Get water data
activate Provider
Provider --> Home: waterIntake, waterGoal,\nwaterGlasses, waterProgress
deactivate Provider

Home -> WaterCard: Render water tracker
activate WaterCard

WaterCard --> User: Display:\n- Water glasses (visual)\n- Current: 5 / 10 glasses\n- 1250ml / 2500ml\n- Progress: 50%

== Add Water ==

User -> WaterCard: Click "+" button\n(or glass icon)

WaterCard -> Provider: addWater(ml: 250)
activate Provider

Provider -> Provider: Increment waterIntake\n(+250ml or +1 glass)
Provider -> Provider: Save to SharedPreferences\nwith today's key: "water_YYYY-MM-DD"
Provider -> Provider: notifyListeners()
Provider --> WaterCard: Water added
deactivate Provider

alt Sync to Cloud
    WaterCard -> Supabase: logWaterIntake(250, today)
    activate Supabase
    Supabase --> WaterCard: Synced
    deactivate Supabase
end

WaterCard --> User: Update UI:\n- 6 / 10 glasses\n- 1500ml / 2500ml\n- 60% progress\n- Animate glass fill

alt Goal Reached
    WaterCard --> User: Show celebration animation\n"🎉 Water goal reached!"
end

== Remove Water ==

User -> WaterCard: Click "-" button

WaterCard -> Provider: removeWater(ml: 250)
activate Provider

Provider -> Provider: Decrement waterIntake\n(-250ml, min: 0)
Provider -> Provider: Save to SharedPreferences
Provider -> Provider: notifyListeners()
Provider --> WaterCard: Water removed
deactivate Provider

WaterCard --> User: Update UI:\n- 5 / 10 glasses\n- 1250ml / 2500ml

== Adjust Water Goal ==

User -> WaterCard: Long press on tracker\nor click settings icon
WaterCard --> User: Show goal adjustment dialog

User -> WaterCard: Adjust goal slider\n(1000ml - 5000ml)
User -> WaterCard: Confirm new goal (e.g., 3000ml)

WaterCard -> Provider: setWaterGoal(3000)
activate Provider
Provider -> Provider: Update waterGoal
Provider -> Provider: Save to SharedPreferences
Provider -> Provider: notifyListeners()
Provider --> WaterCard: Goal updated
deactivate Provider

WaterCard --> User: Update UI:\n- 5 / 12 glasses\n- 1250ml / 3000ml\n- 42% progress

== Configure Water Reminders ==

User -> Home: Navigate to Settings
Home -> ReminderScreen: Open Water Reminder Settings
activate ReminderScreen

ReminderScreen -> Provider: Get reminder settings
activate Provider
Provider --> ReminderScreen: waterRemindersEnabled,\ninterval, start/end times
deactivate Provider

ReminderScreen --> User: Show settings:\n- Enable/Disable toggle\n- Interval: 60 min\n- Start: 8:00 AM\n- End: 10:00 PM

User -> ReminderScreen: Toggle reminders ON
User -> ReminderScreen: Set interval: 90 minutes
User -> ReminderScreen: Set schedule: 7 AM - 9 PM
User -> ReminderScreen: Click "Save"

ReminderScreen -> Provider: updateWaterReminders(\n  enabled: true,\n  intervalMinutes: 90,\n  startHour: 7, startMinute: 0,\n  endHour: 21, endMinute: 0\n)
activate Provider

Provider -> Provider: Save reminder settings\nto SharedPreferences
Provider -> Provider: notifyListeners()
Provider --> ReminderScreen: Settings saved
deactivate Provider

ReminderScreen -> Notify: scheduleWaterReminders(\n  intervalMinutes: 90,\n  startHour: 7, startMinute: 0,\n  endHour: 21, endMinute: 0,\n  title: "💧 Time to hydrate!",\n  body: "Drink a glass of water"\n)
activate Notify

Notify -> Notify: Cancel existing reminders
Notify -> Notify: Calculate reminder times\nwithin schedule window
Notify -> Notify: Schedule periodic notifications\n(every 90 min from 7 AM to 9 PM)
Notify --> ReminderScreen: Reminders scheduled
deactivate Notify

ReminderScreen --> User: Show confirmation:\n"Reminders set! 💧"

deactivate ReminderScreen

== Receive Water Reminder ==

Notify -> User: Push notification\n"💧 Time to hydrate!\nDrink a glass of water"

User -> Notify: Tap notification
Notify -> Home: Open app (to water tracker)
activate Home

Home -> WaterCard: Scroll to water section
WaterCard --> User: Highlight water tracker
deactivate Home

User -> WaterCard: Click "+" to log water
WaterCard -> Provider: addWater(250)

deactivate WaterCard
deactivate Home

note right of Provider
  **Daily Reset:**
  Water intake resets at midnight.
  Each day has its own key:
  - "water_2026-05-20"
  - "water_2026-05-21"

  **Reminder Schedule Example:**
  Start: 7:00 AM
  End: 9:00 PM
  Interval: 90 min

  Notifications at:
  7:00, 8:30, 10:00, 11:30,
  13:00, 14:30, 16:00, 17:30,
  19:00, 20:30
end note

@enduml

